{"tid":30343,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[Benz打手]AMG GTR Nurburgring 7:10.92!!","createTime":"2016-12-09T06:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T15:53:49.000Z","uid":73,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da525831648ccd18a862700e7eba32838f59a4ae","tid":30343,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7oZU2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7oZU2k.jpg&h=3399fcdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cL84587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcL84587.jpg&h=9c983fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMercedes AMG GTR Nurburgring 圈速7:10.92,排第七<br />\nBBA 其餘兩個仲未造到架真正&quot;跑車&quot;出黎<br />\nMercedes 技術明顯超班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPorsche: New 911gt3rs, turbo s 未跑, 但918已經證明自己<br />\nLamborghini: 唔靠Hybrid, LP750sv 用返NA engine, 輕量化車身, 慢918 兩秒, 僅隨其後<br />\nFerrari: 當家馬王Lafa唔拎去跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 488GTB 7:21秒唔知排去邊, 仲好意思叫自己超跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMclaren: P1又係唔見影, Best lap time係四年前嘅mp412c 7:28<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAudi: R8排4x, 圈速我都廢事打<br />\nBmw: 冇Sports Car級別, 最快果架係M4 GTS<br />\nNissan: 神廠, 一部R35威足咁多年, 普通牛馬麥完全唔夠界<br />\nToyota/Lexus: 碌柒喇你咁嘅節奏, turbo engine技術連人地尾燈都見唔到<br />\n<br />\nTesla: P100D 0-100 2.7s<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...搞掂你電池過熱問題跑返圈先講啦<br />\n<br />\n以平民Brand計,Mercedes完全係禁住Audi, BMW黎砌<br />\n就算Sports car以下,new E63s 都係屌打其他房車<br />\n<br />\n一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631f5568d40a167184279850f28af9244d1c1928","tid":30343,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"mercedes 近年既turbo 技術的確係勁<br />\n日本車而家有排追"},{"pid":"c4f9bae345320